<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Baixe o Opera GX e Resgate sua Recompensa</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0b0b0e;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #13131a;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #ff0055;
        }
        .header-banner {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff0055, #990033);
            padding: 35px 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        .logo-area {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .badge {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #ff0055;
            border: 1px solid #ff0055;
        }
        .header-banner h1 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 35px 24px;
        }
        .instructions {
            background: #1c1c24;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: left;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff0055;
        }
        .instructions p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #e1e1e6;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .instructions p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ff0055;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.4);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #ff3377;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.6);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }
        .footer {
            background: #0b0b0e;
            padding: 16px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #666673;
            border-top: 1px solid #1c1c24;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="header-banner">
            <div class="logo-area">🌐</div>
            <span class="badge">Oferta Exclusiva Brasil 🇧🇷</span>
            <h1>Receba sua Recompensa Grátis!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="instructions">
                <p><strong>Siga os passos abaixo:</strong></p>
                <p>1️⃣ Clique no botão abaixo para baixar.</p>
                <p>2️⃣ Instale o navegador <strong>Opera GX</strong>.</p>
                <p>3️⃣ Abra e execute o navegador para liberar seu prêmio.</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- https://saveapp.store/cl/i/ex2o4d -->
            <a href="https://appsave.store/cl/i/ex2o4d" class="btn">Baixar Opera GX Agora</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            Esta é uma campanha promocional independente para computadores e laptops.
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
